Schema Inference Technical Documentation
Overview
The Schema Inference Engine automatically discovers Salesforce object schema from Apex code without requiring Salesforce org connection. It supplements existing XML metadata by analyzing SOQL queries, DML statements, and type declarations.

Architecture
Apex Code → AST → Schema Inference Engine → Inferred Schema
                                    ↓
                         Merge with XML Metadata  
                                    ↓
                          Runtime Execution Context
Core Components
1. Data Structures
InferredField:

type InferredField struct {
    Name         string  // Field API name
    Type         string  // "String", "Integer", "Id", "Datetime", etc.
    IsCustom     bool    // Custom field flag
    ReferenceTo  string  // Target object for lookups
    RelationName string  // Relationship traversal name
    Source       string  // "SOQL", "DML", "TypeDecl"
