Performance
Overhead: <100ms for typical class (50-100 LOC)
Scalability: Linear with code size
Memory: ~1KB per inferred object
Limitations
Regex-based SOQL parsing (may miss edge cases)
Type inference heuristic-based
DML: only infers from first record in bulk operations
